                          "content": "Luxurious beachfront villa in the exclusive Las Rotas area of Dénia. This stunning 4-bedroom property offers breathtaking Mediterranean sea views, a private infinity pool, and direct beach access.\n\nThe villa features modern architecture with floor-to-ceiling windows, spacious open-plan living areas, and a fully equipped gourmet kitchen. Perfect for families or groups seeking an unforgettable coastal retreat.",
